These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, aristoff, montecristo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, pop
1. the fan of folk is the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is between the fan of pop and the aristoff-smoker##2
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Cigar      | aristoff | montecristo | oliveros |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | disco    | pop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
3 different games are played: domino, whist, scrabble
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing domino and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| Game     | whist | scrabble | domino         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, tea
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, daffodil
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person who growsrose and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola     | tea |
| Flower        | rose  | daffodil | dahlia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, blue, ivory
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person who likes green is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person who likes ivory is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Color   | blue  | ivory     | green |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: lime, grapefruit, lemon
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating lime##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Food   | grapefruit | lemon     | lime |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ebony, pink
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who likes pink and the person who likes fuchsia##2
2. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Color   | fuchsia  | ebony   | pink        |
| Sport         | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, pop, soul
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, dutch
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
2. the brazilian is between the fan of soul and the chinese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre          | pop  | jazz  | soul |
| Nationality   | chinese | brazilian | dutch     |

