2. the british is between the person playing poker and the person playing canasta##2
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Game   | canasta   | billiard  | poker  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | mexican |

