.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade, sprite
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person drinking sprite and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Beverage       | sprite | coffee | lemonade  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

