.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, water
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, animation, zombie
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking water and the person watching animation movies##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | water | tea   | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | scientific | animation   |

 